## npm uninstall redux redux-thunk reselect
To be clear, we're still using these packages and need to have them installed. 
However, because Redux Toolkit depends on them, they'll be installed automatically 
when we install @reduxjs/toolkit, 
so we don't need to have the other packages specifically listed in our package.json file.
